#Which of the following are tables within the Chinook database?
Use .help to learn more about SQLite commands!

#List names of possible tables, checklist

#Answer
.tables

Album          Employee       InvoiceLine    PlaylistTrack
Artist         Genre          MediaType      Track        
Customer       Invoice        Playlist  

What is the purpose?
This is there first experience with SQLite and 
running a database.  In the previous slide will be 
the the download instructions and getting started.

This will test if they've got everything setup correctly, 
and if they can log into their database.  They can use .help 
and find that to show the table names in their database they
need to type .tables.  Then they can look and see what tables
exist and match them to the answer.